survey_response.review_text: Had a good experience with Dr Hazra and underwent RCT and crown comfortably. Would highly recommend my friends and family.

Great friendly doctor. I went to the doctor for filling my wisdom tooth.He politely explained the problems I could be facing in my other teeth in future and asked me to be cautious. He explained the medical situation of the particular tooth and filled it quite efficiently without much pain. The clinic also has an instant X-Ray facility so that there is no need for you  to visit  another day with your report.

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you madam. Hope u feel better sooner!

survey_response.review_text: Dr Hazra is super friendly and very helpful. Not only that he carefully listened to all of my problems patiently and then advised me how he is going to treat my condition. He was very easy to talk to and made me understand all the minute details of my medication. I went there alone but I had got zero complain how they operate. To be honest it was a good experience.
Dr. Ramsundar is a great dentist and he took perfect care of all my gum problems. He has an experienced hand with tooth extractions.
This clinic maintains all the possible hygiene, at this present pandemic situation, and specially Dr. Hazra he is a very down to earth and a wonderful person and my experience was very satisfying.
my experience with dr. Ramsundar Hazra was extremely satisfactory. His polite nature steered me out of my fears to ask him questions.I am very content with his treament.

*********** *** **** ***** ****** ** ***** *********The clinic is very hyegenic, doctor explains every issue. Got a filling done at very critical area perfectly.
Location is also perfect in terms of parking your vehicle.
